==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: generic drug
<hw>ge*ner"ic drug`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A medication sold under its
generic name; -- usually legal only after the patent has expired, or if
no patent was issued for the substance. Generic drugs are usually less
expensive than proprietary medications.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>generic name</ent>⟦br⟧
